{"tid":146124,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"心 術 不 正 ！莊 思 敏 驚 蟄 鵝 頸 橋 打 足 7 個 小 人 ！","createTime":"2017-03-06T21:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T09:09:36.000Z","uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc005e4e36476dfa5c6fb17db139174ca3fb6415","tid":146124,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T21:14:18.000Z","msg":"前晚有讀者陳先生透過《蘋果》爆相爆片，見到冇乜化妝嘅莊思敏、同一女友人混入鵝頸橋嘅人潮當中。陳先生表示：「當時見到莊思敏同個女仔friend排隊，佢哋坐低就同小人婆傾咗一輪，之後小人婆開始打啦，見莊思敏個樣有啲緊張咁，定晒神望住小人婆。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打咗10幾分鐘先打完，我打1個都係1分鐘之嘛，之後見莊思敏攞咗張500蚊出嚟，找番150蚊，計小人婆收50蚊一個，即係話佢總共打咗7個人。</span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》事後打俾莊思敏，佢話「驚蟄」打小人其實係自己多年嚟嘅習俗，唔打唔舒服：「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我年年『驚蟄』都要祭白虎o架啦，志在可以擋吓身邊嘅口舌招搖是非。</span></strong>其實我屋企人都有拜開神，年年都會去攝太歲，總之唔同節日就拜唔同嘅神，叫做同佢哋打個招呼。」<br />\n<br />\n對於讀者話佢1個打7個，莊思敏就話：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我嗰日打咗兩份之嘛，其他我朋友打，都冇特定要打邊個嘅，純粹係拜吓神，求個心安理得，我又唔係有咩復仇大計嘅，只係想趕走身邊啲瘟神啫！</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>問莊思敏會唔會順手打埋舊年同佢爆罵戰嘅王宗堯，莊思敏就避而不談話：「呢個人都唔會點見o架啦，同佢可免則免啦，少啲交雜好。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3t227sW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3t227sW.jpg&h=6cb2056d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條女四圍辣火頭都唔係新鮮事<br />\n不過無諗過咁撚爆陰毒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔 乞 人 憎<br />\n打 小 人 嚟 把 撚 ？</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511907e551c586607f6e51d6b40d329fbc81da2e","tid":146124,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bf24836965c6f8139c68ae5f2adc7912d7f4a4","tid":146124,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:58:44.000Z","msg":"可能學波台班癲佬咁去打49000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c8096a30dbb5ddbe0c13e39667bd59c61a64aa","tid":146124,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:59:49.000Z","msg":"打完咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168dd579a8b8ec3b45f28aa40d85ac529722e92a","tid":146124,"uid":75095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:00:17.000Z","msg":"佢真係好撚豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b866dfcb930a8bff12347d44734de4a1b5e244b3","tid":146124,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:01:55.000Z","msg":"年年都keep住有一兩單是非，你應該要還神啦<br />\n唔係根本冇人記得你"},{"pid":"7b2cfa50f4b3a320a0de98c49ef23f77af46f4ce","tid":146124,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:54:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年年都keep住有一兩單是非，你應該要還神啦<br />\n唔係根本冇人記得你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://entretenimento.r7.com/blogs/alvaro-leme/files/2015/08/&Eacute;-tudo-culpa-do-Aecio.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fentretenimento.r7.com%2Fblogs%2Falvaro-leme%2Ffiles%2F2015%2F08%2F%C3%89-tudo-culpa-do-Aecio.gif&h=82f8bec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f9b76c9b503b46c0585ee5b8604ae4dcda909f8","tid":146124,"uid":46563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:09:36.000Z","msg":"仲以為打七警<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}